Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.45,0:00:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.26,0:00:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Over the sky, la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.04,0:00:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.67,0:00:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.26,0:00:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the jet limit
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.09,0:00:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,A heart-warming la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.06,0:00:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The child of science
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.63,0:00:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a million-horsepower engine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.56,0:00:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.53,0:00:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen carefully, la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.55,0:00:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Open your eyes wide
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.20,0:00:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.67,0:00:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be off your guard
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.85,0:00:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,A righteous la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.56,0:00:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The child of science
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.20,0:01:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a seven-force power
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.15,0:01:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.30,0:01:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The Stolen Sun
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.56,0:01:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,London
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.48,0:01:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Sherlock Holmespan Investigation Office
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.98,0:02:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, so this is the artificial sun that's scaring the entire world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.35,0:02:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But a scientist who can create such matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.80,0:02:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Reasoning again, Wacchin?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.90,0:02:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The investigation is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.70,0:02:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Doctor Ochanomizu from Japan's Ministry of Science.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.99,0:02:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Sherlock Holmespan, you are going to Japan by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.55,0:02:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.30,0:02:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You can take this assistance if you want...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.67,0:02:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,A robot? I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.87,0:02:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not that old to get help from a robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.66,0:02:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,My pride wouldn't let me do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.99,0:02:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,My Holmespan family of tradition wouldn't either!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.05,0:02:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so? Robots aren't that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.14,0:02:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.05,0:02:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.85,0:02:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's right, Wacchin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.97,0:02:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There is one thing your robot assistant can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.31,0:02:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.72,0:02:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,As you already know, my house is a mess since I live alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.18,0:03:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you make it clean my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.94,0:03:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Cleaning for my assistant?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.22,0:03:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It suits robots. It doesn't have to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.88,0:03:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,My, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.52,0:03:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You must have gotten even more hatred toward robots after that happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.91,0:03:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokyo
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.55,0:03:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been watching us like that for an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.06,0:03:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, let me go and figure out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.84,0:03:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? No. Hold on, Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.47,0:03:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone must be coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.07,0:04:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it's a real guest this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.03,0:04:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a private detective Sherlock Holmespan from the U.K.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.16,0:04:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,As I expected, it seems like someone's after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.25,0:04:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Doctor Ochanomizu, would you tell me the story?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.38,0:04:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason you made the artificial sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.48,0:04:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely you are not going to deny the fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.78,0:04:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It has already been investigated that you are related to the artificial sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.90,0:04:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You are being rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.98,0:04:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! How dare a robot disrupts a conversation?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.76,0:04:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.48,0:04:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's okay, Atom. -Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.01,0:04:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you, Mr. Holmespan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.90,0:04:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What you said is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.14,0:04:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I made that artificial sun a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.30,0:04:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There used to be a plan to develop Pluto earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.65,0:04:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to develop extreme environments like that of Pluto,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.01,0:05:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,you need a source of strong heat and light.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.10,0:05:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So I created that heat and a light source from plutonium energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.91,0:05:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the artificial sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.73,0:05:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.23,0:05:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,when I finally finished building the artificial sun after three years and five months,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.40,0:05:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,the Pluto development plan got cancelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.23,0:05:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How come? It's such a wonderful plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.89,0:05:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.39,0:05:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They found out that it would cost them more money than planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.91,0:05:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And the artificial sun
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.50,0:05:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I built got forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.67,0:05:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,When I started noticing, someone had already stolen it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.02,0:05:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.80,0:05:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Who would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.94,0:05:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there is a clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.52,0:06:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Ochanomizu, I'm sorry, but please take your clothes off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.28,0:06:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.32,0:06:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Take my clothes off?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.67,0:06:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy's after you. So I have to disguise myself as you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.61,0:06:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.97,0:06:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.16,0:06:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.14,0:06:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop your violence!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.04,0:06:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! You robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.12,0:06:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is amazing. A private detective is a robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.64,0:06:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Me? A robot?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.94,0:06:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! This is a prosthetic hand! I'm human!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Prosthetic hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.28,0:06:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. When I used to work for the British government,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.64,0:06:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I sneaked into a villain's storage to save my colleague.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.15,0:06:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But that was a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.29,0:06:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Tons of dynamites exploded and my body was blown up with the storage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.72,0:06:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I was heavily injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.47,0:06:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time, my doctor was abroad to attend the Doctors' Assembly,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.26,0:07:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,but stupid government. They let a robot doctor take care of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.43,0:07:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Machine is a machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.12,0:07:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't understand human heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.26,0:07:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,They ripped my body apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.15,0:07:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So your body is?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.44,0:07:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The blood of my historic Holmespan family flows in this head only.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So the only original body of yours is your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.15,0:07:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. But I'm human!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.22,0:07:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a man of the Holmespans that
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.14,0:07:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,has achieved a long history of Great Britain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.78,0:07:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.51,0:07:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Doctor. Take your clothes off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.33,0:07:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You should disguise yourself as me and take doctor to a safe place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.19,0:07:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.38,0:07:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk back to me! Robots only need to listen to man's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.94,0:08:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, now the disrupter is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.90,0:08:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing left is a body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.62,0:08:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.50,0:08:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes. I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.94,0:08:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it? Why are you here so late...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.26,0:08:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Doctor Ochanomizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.80,0:08:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but you'll have to come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.24,0:08:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's... It should be fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.65,0:08:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,-Doctor, that's... -Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.70,0:08:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.95,0:08:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, news. Turn on the radio.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.34,0:08:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.74,0:09:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I repeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,In the sky of Kasumigaseki, Tokyo, a sphere with strange light has appeared
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.88,0:09:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and people are getting panicked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.49,0:09:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Cars!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.71,0:09:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.19,0:09:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right. Everyone has run away leaving their cars behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.03,0:09:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, we have no time to delay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.68,0:09:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.10,0:09:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,My gosh. Gasoline caught fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.45,0:09:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-Let's escape to the tunnel. -Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.76,0:09:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.20,0:10:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.49,0:10:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, I'm sorry. You should run first!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.24,0:10:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try to break that artificial sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.52,0:10:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Even if it's you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.41,0:10:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.75,0:10:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The entire Tokyo will be a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.55,0:10:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Energy... My energy's drowning...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.54,0:11:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I safely retrieved the artificial sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.61,0:11:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you think, Doctor Ochanomizu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.58,0:11:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to ask me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.26,0:11:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to order you to make a stronger one than that artificial sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.12,0:11:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.81,0:11:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Using that, I'm going to develop and rule over other planets as well as the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.84,0:11:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.11,0:11:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.75,0:11:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This was in the tentacles of the artificial sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.39,0:11:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This one is Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.60,0:11:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The atom motor must have gotten broken due to high heat; he doesn't even twitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.54,0:11:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.59,0:11:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Atom I trusted is like this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.73,0:12:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I'll cooperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.31,0:12:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a satisfactory answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.91,0:12:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So you are my partner from now on, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.23,0:12:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me prepare a room for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.27,0:12:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the entire universe will be ours if you work with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.03,0:12:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax and take some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.88,0:12:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This is weird for Doctor Ochanomizu to obey so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.68,0:12:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He might be planning something. Watch him carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.67,0:12:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.84,0:12:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Ochanomizu. I mean, Mr. Holmespan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.50,0:12:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Please. Would you change them to other robots' arms and legs?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.22,0:12:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It might not move accordingly,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.47,0:12:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,but I think it will be a help to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.14,0:12:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! I have no intention to get a robot's help!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.31,0:12:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the controller. In a way...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.63,0:13:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Controlling is my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.41,0:13:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like he would listen to any kind of order.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.33,0:13:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm Ochanomizu who built the artificial sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.33,0:13:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I do know, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.68,0:13:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So would you listen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.84,0:13:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.86,0:13:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, then. I will order you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.98,0:13:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Send the artificial sun out to the stratosphere right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.61,0:13:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.63,0:13:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It worked. It's going up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.42,0:14:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Ochanomizu! You can't act on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.60,0:14:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.17,0:14:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, the doctor was controlling...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.22,0:14:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.08,0:14:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let villains like you use the artificial sun as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.76,0:14:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You are not Doctor Ochanomizu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.52,0:14:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You finally noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.32,0:14:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.49,0:14:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a British private detective,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.61,0:14:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sherlock Holmespan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.29,0:14:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.62,0:14:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't miss him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.73,0:14:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot... Chase him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.29,0:14:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, controller robot,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.66,0:14:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a favor to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.48,0:14:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.87,0:14:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to have your arms and legs...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.35,0:15:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's exchange with mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.25,0:15:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Please. I beg you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.10,0:15:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.94,0:15:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. So could you can a welder for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.17,0:15:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't miss him! Don't miss him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.76,0:15:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Capture him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.67,0:15:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Legs... My legs...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.91,0:15:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.32,0:15:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot... When I got shot on my back, it must have ruined the circuit connected to legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.06,0:15:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't be very much far away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.84,0:15:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't miss him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.78,0:15:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.14,0:15:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.71,0:15:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.65,0:15:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you fool us as a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.46,0:15:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.46,0:15:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.51,0:15:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.88,0:16:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Controller robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.60,0:16:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Retrieve the artificial sun to crater!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.25,0:16:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't move right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.45,0:16:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid. You changed your arms and legs with Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.61,0:16:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,How useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.06,0:16:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go! Don't do anything useless! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.39,0:16:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,-Ah, that's! -Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.66,0:16:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,My... I got rid of it but... That controller robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.41,0:16:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no. That robot cannot move.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.39,0:16:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,-What? -I exchanged my arms and legs with his.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.43,0:16:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do? Shoot... My plan's ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.59,0:16:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Who in the world is controlling that artificial sun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.57,0:16:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Piano controlling melody is in my memory...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.70,0:17:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Mind your own business.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.91,0:17:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Get off. Get off!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.74,0:17:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.07,0:17:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You useless robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.75,0:17:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'm going to wait until night and destroy that controller!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.11,0:17:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.37,0:17:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to sneak into that controlling room no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.62,0:17:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Holmespan. Let me carry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.50,0:17:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! I'd rather die than get help from a robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.04,0:17:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Mr. Holmespan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.91,0:18:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot... Dang...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.96,0:18:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Here! Hold on to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.72,0:18:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.09,0:18:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a power to fly nor a million horsepower,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.82,0:18:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,but I have a courage to fight against a bad one!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.47,0:18:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.54,0:18:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-Mr. Holmespan. -Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.76,0:18:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.08,0:18:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,teach me the controlling melody of the artificial sun you remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.80,0:18:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.46,0:18:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to be a genius pianist when I was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.38,0:18:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I should be able to play some music for the controller.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.97,0:18:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Mr. Holmespan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.15,0:19:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,-Mr. Holmespan, here. -All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.25,0:19:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Holmespan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.39,0:19:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-Catch him! -It's Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.32,0:19:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's Holmespan. Don't miss him! -It's Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.06,0:19:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,-Okay then, Atom. -All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.70,0:19:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. I'm going to play until my arms get numb.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.74,0:19:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You will never be able to enter the room!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.31,0:20:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot, Holmespan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.71,0:20:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.09,0:20:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it, Atom. We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.11,0:20:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The artificial sun has finally flown up to space, out of stratosphere!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.42,0:20:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it! We finally did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.05,0:20:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And my dream's gone as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.01,0:20:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Mason!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.12,0:20:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Holmespan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.08,0:20:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Holmespan, Mr. Holmespan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.75,0:20:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.04,0:20:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He got shot in his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.81,0:21:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The only remaining part of him... His precious...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.06,0:21:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,His original body...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.70,0:21:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He got shot in his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.64,0:21:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not forgive!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.89,0:21:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.62,0:21:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.84,0:21:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come! Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.96,0:21:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.14,0:21:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Robot Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.52,0:21:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Wacchin, I wasn't able to be treated by you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.74,0:21:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.30,0:21:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I changed my last body part, and now I'm a robot completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.84,0:21:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Holmespan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.78,0:21:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.47,0:21:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm proud to be a robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.36,0:21:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Robot is just like man...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.96,0:21:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there are robots that are better than men.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.33,0:22:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.45,0:22:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The blood of our proud Holmespan family...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.87,0:22:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Holmespan. Tradition isn't about blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.36,0:22:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about that proper pride in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.62,0:22:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Doctor Wacchin.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.04,0:22:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank that proud child robot Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.59,0:22:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Some unknown package has arrived at Ochanomizu lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.52,0:22:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A disassembled robot was inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.99,0:22:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The assembled robot keeps repeating the words "Aurora Looks".
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.94,0:22:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I visit Penguin Land with Mr. Beard to solve that riddle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.49,0:22:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But there were Black Looks who were
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.05,0:22:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,after robots.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.01,0:22:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Next on Astro Boy. "Black Looks". Look forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.44,0:22:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Next on Astro Boy, "Black Looks"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.67,0:23:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,My arms and legs
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.68,0:23:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,fly over the sky with a jet
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.20,0:23:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.32,0:23:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.07,0:23:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside my waist,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.02,0:23:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,a machine gun's light
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.54,0:23:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.66,0:23:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.82,0:23:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Searchlight's eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.50,0:23:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Laser Blast's hands
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.07,0:23:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven powers, Wa Wa Wa Wa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.29,0:23:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We fight for the peace
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.55,0:24:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go together
